Author: TheObservationalist
Text: You're not. If you're trying to lose weight, the truth is you're going to be very very hungry for awhile until you get used to it. You will get used to it though. I'm 5'4" as well, and honestly even 1500 feels a lot better and still puts me under daily metabolic burn for a normal day. Maybe try that for awhile.

Text: "500 calories is nothing and too much at the same time."  I relate so much omg
